# ── Session working docs: stay on disk, never enter this PUBLIC repo ──
# Ruled 2026-07-20. These are handover/audit notes, not product docs, and
# several carry material that must not be published from a public GitHub repo:
# PHASE1-JOB-SEEKING-CORPUS-MANIFEST quotes a real third party by name from
# private recruiter outreach and lists dated job applications; feedback/ holds
# career-strategy field reports about specific target companies. Model-routing
# rules that allow this content on a cheap LLM path are about ROUTING, not
# PUBLISHING, and do not apply here.
HANDOFF-*.md
PHASE1-*.md
CV-*.md
feedback/
